## 6. EXECUTION ORDER

Build the project in this exact order:

1. **`requirements.txt`** — install all dependencies
2. **`src/config.py`** — all constants and paths
3. **`src/data_loader.py`** — dataset loading
4. **`data/synthetic/generate_synthetic.py`** — run to generate synthetic data
5. **`src/models/sktime_classifiers.py`** — model builders
6. **`src/models/sliding_window.py`** — event detector
7. **`src/evaluation/metrics.py`** — TPR/FPR/ADT metrics
8. **`src/explainability/temporal_importance.py`** — explainability
